&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;A career that’s the whole package!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Conga, we’ve built a community where our colleagues can thrive. Here you’ll find opportunities to innovate and support growth through individual and team development, all within an environment where every voice is heard.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conga&lt;/strong&gt; lines up commercial operations so companies run as connected, smarter businesses. By unifying the people and processes that drive commerce, Conga aligns pricing, quoting, contracting, rebates, and communications so teams stay in sync and buyers keep moving forward. The result is trusted decisions, consistent buyer experiences, and profitable growth. More than 10,000 customers worldwide, including over 50% of the Fortune 100®, trust Conga when commercial complexity is high and global impact is on the line.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title: &lt;/strong&gt;AI Platform Engineer, Business Applications&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Bangalore&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reports to&lt;/strong&gt;: Sr. Manager, Business Applications&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A quick snapshot&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an AI Platform Engineer, to join our dynamic business applications team and contribute to the development of next-generation AI/GenAI based products and capabilities for the consumption within Conga. This role will provide you with the opportunity to own the AI data foundation, enabling scalable AI use cases through RAG pipelines, vector systems, and enterprise data integration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why it’s a big deal…&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will ensure to design, implement RAG pipelines (retrieval, ranking, context injection) and optimize embedding strategies and vector indexing. This role will play a vital role in building real-time batch data and data ingestion pipelines for structured/unstructured sources, develop scalable services using Python, APIs, microservices architecture and integrate with enterprise systems (CRM, KB, data lakes). A strong focus on data governance is required, including enforcing data access policies, masking sensitive information, and ensuring compliance standards. Additionally, the role demands ensuring traceability and auditability of AI outputs, along with deploying and operating services in cloud-native environments with robust logging, monitoring, and AI observability practices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you the person we’re looking for?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Related experience in AI development. &lt;/strong&gt;Your experience of in between 3 to 5 years in software AI development, practices and design patterns. Work with cross-functional teams to ensure quality throughout the software development lifecycle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills and Tools.&lt;/strong&gt; You have expertise as a AI developer using Python, FastAPI, PyTest, Celery and other Python frameworks and high-level familiarity with AI/ML, GenAI, and MLOps concepts. You also have hands-on experience with object-oriented programming, concurrency, design patterns, and REST APIs. Your hands-on experience with RAG, vector databases. Familiarity with Kubernetes, CI/CD tooling such as Terraform and GitHub Actions. Working knowledge of logging, monitoring, and AI observability practices (e.g., tracing LLM calls, retrieval metrics, model performance dashboards).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cloud Service Provider.&lt;/strong&gt; You have experience of any of the cloud platforms such as AWS, MS Azure and GCP.&lt;/p&gt;
