&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Quick Snapshot&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Conga is seeking a talented APAC Partner Marketing Manager to join our passionate and dynamic team of partner marketers. This key role will see you work cross-functionally with a variety of teams to build and scale marketing campaigns and activities with our largest global partners, and crucial regional partners. In this role, you will be responsible for defining, creating, executing and bringing go-to-market (GTM) strategies to life as you build deep relationships across our partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why It&#39;s a Big Deal&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Principal Partner Marketing Manager, you will play a crucial role in defining the GTM strategies and building a deep relationship with our partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are You the Person We&#39;re Looking For?&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience.&lt;/strong&gt; You must have more than 12 years of experience in Partner Marketing enablement within B2B software space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marketing Activities.&lt;/strong&gt; You are excellent in creating and executing marketing activities such as webinars and other online and in-person event activities, to support integrated campaigns. You craft and develop marketing content for compelling joint solution offerings with strategic partner accounts including creation of required marketing assets (product videos, customer success stories, demos, presentations, how-to guides etc.).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GSI/RSI partnership.&lt;/strong&gt; You know how to help engagement teams understand the value proposition of the Conga-GSI/RSI partnership through a multichannel approach that encompasses digital, events, training, enablement and more!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Business Partnership.&lt;/strong&gt; You will partner closely with business teams to deeply understand their challenges, priorities, and operational needs, ensuring analytics solutions directly address real business problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross functional collaboration.&lt;/strong&gt; You work closely with the teams below to drive awareness of the partnerships&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conga Corporate Marketing team, &lt;/strong&gt;to create thought leadership opportunities, maximize the partners’ presence on conga.com and insert the partners into key Conga events.&lt;/p&gt;
