&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;Conga is looking for a Senior Product Manager to own the strategy, roadmap, and execution for our Rebate Management solution — a mission-critical product serving enterprise customers in distribution, manufacturing, and CPG who manage complex, high-stakes trading-partner programs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;This is a high-autonomy, high-accountability role. You&#39;ll define what gets built, why, and how it wins in the market — working across a complex web of accrual models, program structures, and settlement workflows, and translating that complexity into a product that is both commercially differentiated and operationally excellent.&lt;/p&gt;
